commentText: Modify the application context's internal bean factory after its standard_initialization. All bean definitions will have been loaded, but no beans_will have been instantiated yet. This allows for overriding or adding_properties even to eager-initializing beans._@param beanFactory the bean factory used by the application context_@throws org.springframework.beans.BeansException in case of errors
